There was more Italian in that cappuccino than a whole meal at Ruffino's.
Now, I'm watching Tony Bourdain in Naples just to make up for the rest of the evening..
I hope I can get another chance to go here and have them prove me wrong, but I won't do it on my dime.
There was just a little too much Olive Garden in Ruffino's to justify the prices.

